<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.3.10">
<l>vaṇṭu taṇṭē ṉuṇṭu vāḻum vatari neṭumālai</l>
<l>kaṇṭal vēli maṅkai vēntaṉ kaliya ṉolimālai</l>
<l>koṇṭu toṇṭarp pāṭi yāṭak kūṭi ṭiṉīḷvicumpil</l>
<l>aṇṭa mallāl maṟṟa varkkō rāṭci yaṟiyōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If devotees wholeheartedly join to sing and dance,</l>
<l rend="indent">taking up [this] garland of words</l>
<l>Of Kaliyaṉ, king of Maṅkai with screw pine hedges,</l>
<l>On tall Māl of Badarī where dwell bees sipping fresh nectar,</l>
<l>We don’t believe that the domain for them will be other than heaven</l>
<l rend="indent">in the lofty skies.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
